## 6. 数据库查询语句

**Mapper文件路径**: `/Users/allwe/workspace/waimai_service_bizad_billing_server/src/main/java/com/sankuai/meituan/waimai/bizad/platform/billing/mapper/sdf/WmAdSdfRatioConfigFutureMapper.java`

**关键查询方法**：

```java
// 查询指定日期所有待生效记录，按商家分组取最新一条
@Update("UPDATE wm_ad_sdf_ratio_config_future 
         SET status = 1, 
             prev_cash_ratio = #{prevCashRatio}, 
             utime = unix_timestamp() 
         WHERE id = #{id}")
void updatePrevRatioAndSetEffective(@Param("id") long id, 
                                    @Param("prevCashRatio") BigDecimal prevCashRatio);

// 更新签约表的比例
@Update("UPDATE wm_ad_sdf_sign 
         SET cash_ratio_decimal = #{cashRatioDecimal}, 
             utime = unix_timestamp() 
         WHERE partner_id = #{partnerId} 
           AND partner_type = #{partnerType} 
           AND status = 1")
int updateSignCashRatioDecimal(@Param("partnerId") long partnerId, 
                               @Param("partnerType") int partnerType, 
                               @Param("cashRatioDecimal") BigDecimal cashRatioDecimal);
```

