# 随单返首页弹窗一键开启 Implementation Plan

**Goal:** 在已有 getSdfSignInfo RPC 和 sign HTTP 两个接口上做最小扩展，支持首页弹窗签约场景
**Architecture:** billing-client（枚举+DTO新增字段）→ billing-server（计算逻辑+signSourceCode透传）→ billing-api（HTTP入参读取）；三仓库按依赖顺序实现
**Tech Stack:** Java/Maven, Thrift RPC, Spring MVC, Mockito 单元测试

---

## Interface Contracts

### C1: `SdfSignInfoDTO` 新增 field 14-16
> Provider: T1 | Consumer: T3

```java
// billing-client: SdfSignInfoDTO.java
// 新增3个 optional String 字段（在现有field 13 ratioInfo之后）
private String redPacketIssueDays;    // field 14
private String redPacketInflationRate; // field 15
private String transferInRatio;        // field 16
// + getters/setters
```

### C2: `SdfSignSourceEnum.C_POP_UP_WINDOW(3)`
> Provider: T1 | Consumer: T5

```java
// billing-client: SdfSignSourceEnum.java
C_POP_UP_WINDOW(3, "C端首页弹窗签约"),
```

