## Task List

### T1: billing-client — 新增 SdfSignSourceEnum 枚举值 + SdfSignInfoDTO 字段 【Type B】

Files:
- `src/main/java/com/sankuai/meituan/waimai/bizad/billing/platform/domain/sdf/SdfSignSourceEnum.java`
